      "raw_text": "1t is currently understood around\nthe city hall today that Mayor Pratt\nIs about to announce the removal\nof Water Commissioner Arvid Reu-\nterdahl. The change will be, 1t is\ngiven out, failure to support the\nmayor in his policies.\n\n\nThe most recent offense that\nReuterdahl has committed was his\nexposure Of the effort of the board\nof public works to unload on the\ncity a dirt fill reservoir plastered\nover with thin layer of cement at\na cost of 100000. 1t is said such\na reservoir can be built for 5000.\nReuterdahl at the meeting Of the\ncity council last night said that he\nwould not accept the responsibility\nIf such a reservoir were built, that\n1t was contrary to the recommends\ntions of Professor Burr. and prac-\ntically waste of money for the\ncity."
    }
  ]
